<pre>
 s = 1 + 2 + 4 + 8 + 16 + ...

   = 1 + 2(1 + 2 + 4 + 8 + ...)

   = 1 + 2s,

so

-1 = 1 + 2 + 4 + 8 + 16 + ...
</pre>
<p>(Regular summation gives a sum of infinity, but the idea above <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/1_%2B_2_%2B_4_%2B_8_%2B_%E2%8B%AF">does make a certain sense</a>.)</p>
<p>(Thanks, Murtadha.)</p>
